      "name": "Visa Timeline/Active",
      "context": "Visa Timeline card - Active state. Displays info about the currently selected WHV 417 visa from /api/visas endpoint. Shows: visa label (e.g. WHV 417 - Year 1), days remaining before visa expires, a progress bar showing % of visa duration elapsed, start date and end date. Uses warning/orange theme. Data source: selected visa from visa dropdown selector in page header. The visa selector drives which visa data is shown across the whole dashboard.",
