    {
      "type": "frame",
      "id": "Vtpka",
      "x": 1026,
      "y": 716,
      "name": "This Week",
      "context": "This Week card - Shows current week work hours summary. Displays: total hours logged this week, a 7-bar mini chart (Mon-Sun) showing hours per day, and bottom info with remaining hours needed and weekly goal. BAR COLOR RULES (4 tiers): == 0h → $--secondary (no work); <= 5h → #a5b4fc light indigo (low); <= 8h → $--primary (medium/normal); > 8h → #3730a3 dark indigo (high/above goal). Bar height is proportional to hours (max ~40px for 10h+). Hour label above each bar matches bar color. Example data: Mon=8h ($--primary), Tue=4h (light), Wed=3h (light), Thu=10h (dark), Fri=9h (dark), Sat=0h, Sun=0h. Data from work entries logged for the current calendar week.",
