      "name": "Visa Date Picker / Calendar",
      "context": "Visa Date Picker / Calendar — Default state (no blocked ranges). Shows a monthly calendar with prev/next navigation header, weekday row (Mo–Su), and a 6-week grid. Currently showing March 2025 with day 15 selected (filled with $--primary color, white text). Available days are fully interactive. In React: powered by shadcn/ui Calendar (DayPicker). Props: selected (Date), onSelect (Date => void), blockedRanges (Array<{ start, end, visaOrdinal }> — empty in this default state). Day underline bars appear only when blockedRanges is non-empty (see Visa Date Picker / Calendar / Blocked Range). Day colors for visa ordinals: 1st=$--visa-1st-color, 2nd=$--visa-2nd-color, 3rd=$--visa-3rd-color.",
