    {
      "type": "frame",
      "id": "yBAhv",
      "x": 44,
      "y": 7039,
      "name": "Hours - Desktop",
      "context": "## Weekly Grid (Hours View)\n\n### Purpose\nMonthly overview of work hours in a compact weekly grid. Rows = weeks. Expandable employer breakdown per week.\n\n### Business Rules\n- Eligible Hours = only hours from employers with isEligible=true\n- Eligible Days = WEEKLY threshold conversion:\n  - 30+ h/week → 7d | 24-29h → 4d | 18-23h → 3d | 12-17h → 2d | 6-11h → 1d | <6h → 0d\n- Calculation is per-visa: a week spanning 2 visas splits eligible hours by visa date range\n\n### Visa Color System\n- 1st Visa: green ($--visa-1st-color #10b981)\n- 2nd Visa: blue ($--visa-2nd-color #3b82f6)\n- 3rd Visa: amber ($--visa-3rd-color #f59e0b)\n- No visa: neutral gray ($--muted)\n- Left accent border on expanded week row\n- Per-day colored dots under daily hours (only for multi-visa weeks)\n- Boundary badges: 'first' / 'last' on visa transition days\n\n### Split Week (spanning 2 visas)\n- Visa column shows 2 colored dots\n- Eligible/Days show split: '12h - 18h' and '2d - 3d' with per-visa colored dots\n- Total column stays single value\n\n### Grid Structure (NEW column order)\n- Header: Week | Visa | Total Hours | Eligible Hours | Eligible Days | separator | Mon-Sun | Actions\n- Vertical separator between aggregate stats and daily data\n- Chevron in Week column (left side), Edit pencil in Actions column (right side)\n- Week rows: collapsed by default, expandable via chevron click\n- Empty days: dash '–' | Empty eligible/days: dash '–'\n\n### Week States Shown\n1. Collapsed with data (single visa) - Feb 23-Mar 1, Mar 23-29\n2. Expanded with employer breakdown - Mar 2-8\n3. Collapsed with split visa + boundary badges - Mar 9-15\n4. Empty (no hours logged) - Mar 16-22\n\n### Employer Breakdown (expanded)\n- Industry icon (16px colored square) + employer name + eligibility dot (green/red 4px)\n- Total hours per employer\n- Daily hours per employer aligned with day columns\n\n### Interactions\n- Chevron expand/collapse: shows employer breakdown per week\n- Pencil icon per row: navigates to /hours/edit?week=YYYY-MM-DD\n- Edit Hours button: navigates to /hours/edit\n- Month/Year dropdown pickers + Prev/Next arrows\n\n### Design Tokens\n- Background: $--background | Card: $--card | Border: $--border\n- Text: $--foreground (primary), $--muted-foreground (secondary)\n- Expanded week bg: #F8F6FF | Accent: $--primary\n- Font: Inter, sizes 8-24px\n- Grid card: 10px radius, subtle shadow",
      "width": 960,
      "fill": "$--background",
      "layout": "vertical",
      "children": [
